headline: Autodesk’s AI Prosthetics Partnership Could Be A Game Changer For Autodesk (ADSK)
summary: On February 24, 2026, Autodesk announced a partnership with prosthetics company BioDapt to use its AI-enabled Fusion platform to redesign and scale high-performance prosthetic systems for para athletes preparing for the Los Angeles 2028 Games and wider use beyond elite sport.
